{{!--
/**
 * Spell Comparison Dialog Template
 *
 * PURPOSE:
 * Side-by-side comparison interface for analyzing multiple spells simultaneously.
 * Displays spell properties in tabular format with highlighting for differences,
 * providing users with detailed comparative analysis for spell selection and
 * strategic planning. Supports empty state when no spells are selected.
 *
 * CONTEXT REQUIREMENTS:
 * @param {Array<Object>} spells - Array of spells being compared
 * @param {string} spells[].name - Spell display name
 * @param {string} spells[].enrichedIcon - HTML for spell icon/image display
 * @param {Object} comparisonData - Processed comparison data structure
 * @param {Array<Object>} comparisonData.properties - Array of comparable properties
 * @param {string} comparisonData.properties[].name - Property display name
 * @param {Array<Object>} comparisonData.properties[].values - Property values per spell
 * @param {string} comparisonData.properties[].values[].value - Formatted property value
 * @param {boolean} comparisonData.properties[].values[].highlight - Whether to highlight differences
 *
 * ACCESSIBILITY FEATURES:
 * - Semantic table structure with proper thead/tbody sections
 * - Table headers with spell information for column identification
 * - Row headers for property names with proper scope
 * - Highlighted cells for visual difference indication
 * - Empty state with descriptive message for no selections
 *
 * CUSTOMIZATION POINTS:
 * - Table displays dynamically based on selected spells
 * - Property comparison highlights differences between spells
 * - Empty state provides guidance when no spells selected
 * - Spell icons and names clearly identify each comparison column
 * - Highlighting system draws attention to important differences
 *
 * INTEGRATION:
 * - Used for spell analysis and selection assistance
 * - Connects to spell comparison and analysis systems
 * - Uses module localization keys from SPELLBOOK.Comparison namespace
 * - Supports strategic spell selection and planning workflows
 */
--}}

<div class="spell-comparison-content">
  {{#if spells.length}}
    <!-- Spell Comparison Table -->
    <table class="comparison-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th></th> <!-- Empty header for property names column -->
          {{#each spells}}
            <!-- Spell Header Column -->
            <th class="spell-header">
              <div class="spell-info">
                {{{enrichedIcon}}}
                <span class="spell-name">{{name}}</span>
              </div>
            </th>
          {{/each}}
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each comparisonData.properties}}
          <tr>
            <!-- Property Name Row Header -->
            <td class="property-name">{{name}}</td>

            <!-- Property Values for Each Spell -->
            {{#each values}}
              <td class="property-value {{#if highlight}}highlighted{{/if}}">
                {{value}}
              </td>
            {{/each}}
          </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  {{else}}
    <!-- Empty Comparison State -->
    <div class="empty-comparison">
      <p>{{localize "SPELLBOOK.Comparison.NoSpellsSelected"}}</p>
    </div>
  {{/if}}
</div>
